cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR 

This paper discusses active learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper mentions applications such as text analysis, image recognition, and social network modeling, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also proposes a general active learning framework that can be applied to any data structure, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper presents experimental results on benchmark datasets, which is a common practice in the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG).
